process.builders

Class RandomAutomatonBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • process.builders.RandomAutomatonBuilder

  • public class RandomAutomatonBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder that allows to create a random automaton with parameters to specify. Default automaton generated creates an automaton with one initial state and one final state
    Author:
    Aldric Vitali Silvestre

      • build

        public Automaton build()
        Build the random automaton with the help of all parameters set by user. WARNING ! This method cannot produce automatons with multiple initial states.
        Returns:
        the randomly builded automaton

      • buildSilly

        public Automaton buildSilly()
        This build method is unlikely to produce always good results, so be careful using it with big automatons. Build the random automaton with the help of all parameters set by user.
        Returns:
        a new Random automaton
